snippet.title: Billy Bear Visits Luey ! (Dos game 1996)
snippet.description:
Billy Bear Visits Luey ! is a MS-DOS eduational storybook game (or program)
Merely, if you read the storybook, you click a left or right button.
In addition to that, if you click other things, the things act interestingly.

By the way, from 00:36, the voice function is very odd and eccentric. 
Listen to it !!
